item.description: I’m always interested in the music that’s the best to come out in any given year, but this often contrasts heavily with my actual listening habits. This is why I look to Last.

item.title: AOTY2019
item.description: It’s the time of year where I talk about way more than anyone is willing to care about… the ALBUM OF THE YEAR. I keep track all year, every year, and 2019 has been no different.
